    headline: 'OpenLeash vs OAuth for AI Agent Authorization',
    description: 'Compare OAuth token-based delegation with OpenLeash per-action authorization for AI agents. Learn why OAuth scopes aren\'t enough for autonomous agents and how the two systems complement each other.',
